Module jakarta.data.api
Package jakarta.data.repository

Interface CrudRepository<T,​K>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the bean type
    K - the key type
    All Superinterfaces:
    DataRepository<T,​K>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    PageableRepository<T,​K>
    public interface CrudRepository<T,​K>
extends DataRepository<T,​K>

    Interface for generic CRUD operations on a repository for a specific type.

        <S extends T> S save​(S entity)
        Saves a given entity. Use the returned instance for further operations as the save operation might have changed the entity instance completely.
        Type Parameters:
        S - type of entity to save
        Parameters:
        entity - the entity to be saved
        Returns:
        the saved entity; will never be null.
        Throws:

      • findAllById

        Stream<T> findAllById​(Iterable<K> ids)
        Returns all instances of the type T with the given IDs.

        If some or all ids are not found, no entities are returned for these IDs.

        Note that the order of elements in the result is not guaranteed.

        Parameters:
        ids - must not be null nor contain any null values.
        Returns:
        guaranteed to be not null. The size can be equal or less than the number of given ids.
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - in case the given ids or one of its items is null.

        void deleteAllById​(Iterable<K> ids)
        Deletes all instances of the type T with the given IDs.
